{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/RollAndBounce.png?t=1734225516\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of bouncy fluffballs and conquer twisting, dynamic levels! Master precision controls and fast reflexes as you zip through courses filled with surprising obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/GameplayGif.gif?t=1734225516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/Title2.png?t=1734225516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect coins scattered across each level to unlock new customization options for your fluffball. Track down every coin in a world to earn special rewards and take your fluff style to the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/CustomizeYourFluff.png?t=1734225516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/BounceBack.png?t=1734225516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brace yourself\u2014Fluff\u2019n\u2019Roll is not for the faint-hearted! Each level presents tougher terrain, with new obstacles and hazards that push your skills to the limit. Every failure is a lesson. Master each course, learn the terrain, and perfect your fluffball skills with every try.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/HammerHit.gif?t=1734225516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3321020?t=17342